Permanent coordination and control with a view to determining the annual water use of the Krishna basin.
The Committee was constituted vide Reference No. The decision has been taken by the government of 1.
The Superintendent Engineer, Inter State River Arbitration Office, Pune referred to No. obtained under 2.
As per the proposal, the list of members of the Standing Coordination and Control Committee is being changed.
The revised composition of the Committee shall be as follows: -
